title: Lone Ranger ISO
description:
This is an ISO ready to burn to DVD. It contains all the Lone Ranger movies ever made (NOT the Republic serial, just the actual movies), from the 1949 T.V. pilot starring Clayton Moore and Jay Silverheels, to the 2013 abomination starring Johnny Depp (who, by the way, was the only white man to ever portray Tonto on the screen).

Enter the Lone Ranger (1949 B&W)
The Lone Ranger (1956)
The Lone Ranger and the Lost City of Gold (1958)
The Legend of the Lone Ranger (1981)
The Lone Ranger (2013)
